<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Vorteile</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Nachteile</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Keine Blockierung durch PVCs</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Komplexe Implementation</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Kleine Caches</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Zus=C3=A4tzlicher Dienst erforderlich</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Cleanup: inkrementell nach Usage</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Datentransfer (copy) vor und nach dem Build</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div><p><strong>Processing Overhead</strong>: ~ 11s (~ 3s (Query+Download)=
