n pro Monat</strong>: ~ USD 1.24 (Annahme: 10 Repos mit je 10 Cache Entries=
 =C3=A0 500M =3D 50GB; 400 Builds pro Monat (=E2=86=92 4 COPY/LIST/PUT Oper=
ations pro Build + je 1GB Datentransfer))</p><p class=3D"auto-cursor-target=
