 0s</p><p class=3D"auto-cursor-target"><strong>Kosten pro Monat</strong>: ~=
 CHF 117 (fix pro Namespace; 5G Cache Size + zus=C3=A4tzliche CPU + Memory =
f=C3=BCr Varnish Pods)</p></td>
